Fy_haxor Made by FalO

This is pretty basic map.
Terrorists must plant the bomb in to the bombsite at the pool. And CTs must of course prevent it from happening.

Recommened players 4 - 40

There are many secret areas in the map, and the code to the door is... well you just have to figure it out yourself :D

the vending machines work! bottles will come out if you press the buttons in the vending machine.

have fun!
